      <title>摩根大通卷入芝加哥最古老酒店之一的争夺战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/jpmorgan-dragged-into-fight-over-one-of-chicago-s-oldest-hotels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通旗下的一个子公司因一笔未偿还的 3.33 亿美元贷款而陷入法律纠纷，这笔贷款由芝加哥市中心最大、最古老的酒店之一希尔顿帕尔默酒店 (Hilton Palmer House) 担保。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/jpmorgan-dragged-into-fight-over-one-of-chicago-s-oldest-hotels</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 16:11:44 GMT</pubDate>
